-We're headed for a tunnel.
-Oh, yeah.

00:59:30.269 --> 00:59:31.478
Full speed ahead.

00:59:38.277 --> 00:59:41.154
-How can they see where they're going?
-They can't.

00:59:41.655 --> 00:59:43.656
There's no knowing
where they're going.

00:59:44.033 --> 00:59:45.283
Switch on the lights!

01:00:12.895 --> 01:00:14.437
People, keep an eye out.

01:00:14.605 --> 01:00:16.731
We're passing some
very important rooms here.

01:00:22.321 --> 01:00:23.863
What do you use hair cream for?

01:00:25.032 --> 01:00:26.699
To lock in moisture.

01:00:30.287 --> 01:00:32.413
[MOOING]

01:00:33.874 --> 01:00:36.376
-Whipped cream.
-Precisely.

01:00:37.128 --> 01:00:38.294
That doesn't make sense.

01:00:39.463 --> 01:00:41.172
For your information, little girl...

01:00:41.340 --> 01:00:45.176
...whipped cream isn't whipped cream at
all unless it's been whipped with whips.

01:00:45.344 --> 01:00:47.470
Everybody knows that.

01:01:37.062 --> 01:01:40.023
Stop the boat.
I wanna show you guys something.

01:02:00.794 --> 01:02:04.047
Now, this is the most important room
in the entire factory.

01:02:04.506 --> 01:02:08.676
Now, everyone, enjoy yourselves,
but just don't touch anything.

01:02:08.844 --> 01:02:10.094
Okay? Go on.

01:02:10.304 --> 01:02:11.596
Go on, scoot.

01:02:23.108 --> 01:02:24.943
Hey, Mr. Wonka, what's this?

01:02:25.945 --> 01:02:29.113
Oh. Let me show you.

01:02:30.950 --> 01:02:32.200
Thank you.

01:02:32.368 --> 01:02:34.535
These are Everlasting Gobstoppers.

01:02:34.703 --> 01:02:37.413
They're for children who are given
very little allowance.

01:02:37.581 --> 01:02:41.000
