Listen close, and listen hard

01:08:05.242 --> 01:08:07.118
To the tale of Violet Beauregarde

01:08:07.286 --> 01:08:09.829
This gentle girl
She sees no wrong

01:08:09.997 --> 01:08:12.415
In chewing, chewing, chewing, chewing

01:08:12.583 --> 01:08:21.966
Chewing, chewing all day long

01:08:23.468 --> 01:08:24.802
Yeah

01:08:34.062 --> 01:08:36.355
She goes on chewing till, at last

01:08:36.523 --> 01:08:38.649
Her chewing muscles grow so vast

01:08:38.817 --> 01:08:41.152
And from her face
Her giant chin

