01:10:10.575 --> 01:10:11.867
There's too much to see.

01:10:12.035 --> 01:10:13.077
-Mr. Wonka?
-Yeah?

01:10:13.370 --> 01:10:15.079
Why did you decide to let people in?

01:10:15.330 --> 01:10:17.289
So they could see the factory,
of course.

01:10:17.499 --> 01:10:19.875
