01:11:57.265 --> 01:11:59.016
I see.

01:11:59.392 --> 01:12:01.310
These flashbacks happen often?

01:12:01.478 --> 01:12:03.437
Increasingly...

01:12:03.730 --> 01:12:05.064
...today.

