01:13:38.617 --> 01:13:42.161
...and two parakeets and three canaries
and a green parrot and a turtle...

01:13:42.329 --> 01:13:45.497
...and a silly old hamster.
I want a squirrel!

01:13:45.916 --> 01:13:47.166
All right, pet.

01:13:47.334 --> 01:13:50.044
Daddy will get you a squirrel
as soon as he possibly can.

01:13:50.211 --> 01:13:53.756
