I want a trained squirrel.

01:13:55.091 --> 01:13:56.675
Very well.

01:13:57.010 --> 01:14:00.179
Mr. Wonka, how much do you want
for one of these squirrels?

01:14:00.347 --> 01:14:02.306
Name your price.

01:14:03.183 --> 01:14:05.809
Oh, they're not for sale.
She can't have one.

01:14:10.815 --> 01:14:12.399
Daddy.

01:14:14.069 --> 01:14:15.319
